Change: Introduced mbam-api/src/authentication as the centralized authentication boundary.
Debugging: Mapped duplicated JWT parsing in business, business-unit, product, team, transaction, and sync routes.
Implementation: Added legacy/keycloak provider selection, Keycloak token introspection, audience validation, immutable subject mapping, verified-email migration linking, and complete baseline-role alignment.
